  BTN S2:  0x01  released
  FF0010 IntEn:  0x00  UART RX IRQ: disabled
  FF0100 UART:   status=0x02  RX ready: no  CTS: yes  TX busy: no
  UART TX log:   "_h:\r\n bra _h\r\n"
